feedback.name: F***O
feedback.content: Arrived well to Cuernavaca, Mexico, took 15 days to arrive, do not pay extra customs cost, the equipment looks great with the big screen, it does not work with an athletic network like (Bait) because the team does not have the B28 Network (700 Mhz) It can only be used in that company with calls but no mobile data, with all the others (Telcel, at& T, Movistar) if you work well with data and calls, en dual SIM and apart brings space for micro SD (not included) the team arrived with gift screen protector, Transparent silicone case, charger, type C cable, manuals, SIM pull key and adapter, by connecting it to the internet you got a system update it is very good the equipment for those who like big screens, I am very satisfied and recommend the seller, thanks
